  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK163">
<l>aṟaṉākkam vēṇṭātā ṉeṉpāṉ piṟaṉākkam</l>
<l>pēṇā taḻukkaṟup pāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of him who instead of rejoicing in the wealth of others, envies it, it will be said "he neither desires virtue not wealth."</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
